      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the chicken is cooking, peel and finely chop your <strong>brown onion[s]</strong></p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
