    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chopped spinach, halved cherry tomatoes </strong>and <strong>grated cheese</strong> to the orzo with <strong>half</strong> the <strong>torn basil</strong> (save the rest for later!) and cook for a further 1-2 min or until the spinach has wilted</p><p>Once wilted, give everything a good mix up – this is <strong>one-pot creamy free range chicken thigh florentine</strong></p>",
